OL,4,G2100FA History of Britain by Simon
OL,5,     FSchama
OL,6,     GSimon Schama looks beyond the
OL,7,     Gromantic stories of Cavaliers and
OL,8,     GRoundheads to the real story of
OL,9,     Gthe English Civil War, in which
OL,10,     Ghundreds of thousands died.
OL,11,G2200FDogs of War - Storyville
OL,12,     GFilm about a seemingly ordinary
OL,13,     GEnglishman who spent more than 40
OL,14,     Gyears as a mercenary.
OL,15,G2330FThe Empire State Story - Timewatch
OL,16,     GFirst transmitted in 2001, this
OL,17,     Gprogramme chronicles the
OL,18,     Gconstruction of the Empire State
OL,19,     GBuilding in New York, which was
OL,20,     Gthe world's tallest skyscraper
OL,21,     Gwhen opened in 1931.
